godoc servey

Overview

godoc can autogenerates documents from the comments of the source files

It works on packages, not individual functions

Syntax:

Works like markdown

Comments preceeding package definition will be the overview of the package

Comments preceeding functions and constants will be descriptions of them

// with nothing means change line

two spaces means code area

How to list bugs in godoc?

    BUG(y): array won't work

Make a server and allows query with godoc [package] -q

    godoc -http=:6060 -index